@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ztvdsw(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = ((v2 + (v0 + 0.10 / v0 + 0.72)) + ((v2 + 0.78 + v0 + 0.14) * wp.exp(v2 + 0.39)))
    v1 = (wp.exp(wp.sin(v2 + 0.81)) * (0.65 - (v2 + 0.69 / v2 + 0.58)))
    v2 = (v1 / (wp.abs(tmp + 0.83) + (v0 + 0.05 / v1 + 0.83)))
    v0 = (wp.abs((tmp + 0.75 - v0 + 0.86)) / 0.43)
    tmp = v1
    data[tid] = v0
